  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lost Hope</strong> is a horror game based on the Backroooms universe, where you have to solve puzzles to progress through the story, explore mysterious places filled with strange and incomprehensible things, and the locals won't let you leave the place so easily, if there is any way out at all...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Based On the Backrooms Universe.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><i>All levels were made by hand.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/148ddf3372d20b65966fbd5318f51c2f.webp?t=1774093204\" width=256 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an exciting journey through more than 20+ different levels. In each level, a thrilling story intertwines with challenging puzzles, offering different escape routes fraught with danger at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/a5ee0d0b1bbe743932f7c4ef96c28f21.poster.avif?t=1774093204\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/a5ee0d0b1bbe743932f7c4ef96c28f21.webm?t=1774093204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/a5ee0d0b1bbe743932f7c4ef96c28f21.mp4?t=1774093204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/ffdf46cacf5a15bec25044e82b58a0c3.webp?t=1774093204\" width=256 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dive into the exciting story, which unfolds in an abandoned laboratory Last Hope inc., where you will play as one character to uncover the story of the other.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you be able to reveal all the secrets of this place?</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/0f4d68eccdb55b482e89c014222dd6af.poster.avif?t=1774093204\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/0f4d68eccdb55b482e89c014222dd6af.webm?t=1774093204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/0f4d68eccdb55b482e89c014222dd6af.mp4?t=1774093204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/3a51bdb64aa263bbedf000cff295460c.webp?t=1774093204\" width=256 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Face more than 5+ entities, each with its own feature and mechanics. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Knowledge of each entity will help you progress through the levels and storyline.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Will you be able to escape this place in one piece?</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/5c57261b4286648a8cc35025fda92077.avif?t=1774093204\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras_big/5c57261b4286648a8cc35025fda92077.avif?t=1774093204 width=800 height=450 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Also the game features a <strong>No Entity Mode</strong> if you want to just explore levels without being hunted.</p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Lost Hope</strong> is a horror game based on the Backroooms universe, where you have to solve puzzles to progress through the story, explore mysterious places filled with strange and incomprehensible things, and the locals won't let you leave the place so easily, if there is any way out at all...  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Based On the Backrooms Universe.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  <br><i>All levels were made by hand.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/148ddf3372d20b65966fbd5318f51c2f.webp?t=1774093204\" width=256 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Embark on an exciting journey through more than 20+ different levels. In each level, a thrilling story intertwines with challenging puzzles, offering different escape routes fraught with danger at every turn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/a5ee0d0b1bbe743932f7c4ef96c28f21.poster.avif?t=1774093204\" width=692 height=388 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/a5ee0d0b1bbe743932f7c4ef96c28f21.webm?t=1774093204\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/a5ee0d0b1bbe743932f7c4ef96c28f21.mp4?t=1774093204\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2600830/extras/ffdf46cacf5a15bec25044e82b58a0c3.webp?t=1774093204\" width=256 height=32 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_pa